
Note: Before reading this book, I want to warn/clarify a couple of things:1) Some of you will be confused as to who will be falling in love with Bora in the story. Well here's the answer: YOU!! You will be the one who will love her and stuff.2) Some chapters/content of the writing will change depending on your sex (female/male). That's also a reason I put the tags "lesbian","straight", and "bisexual" just in case you feel offended (although you shouldn't really). Of course you can read both sides of the story as freely as you wish.3) The story has content that is sexual and violent. I obviously rated it for mature. However, don't be surprised if the content is a little too explicit/detailed.4) Enjoy!!